titleNullable: One Piece Episode and Production Info
subtitleNullable: This dataset contains each episode production info and manga chapter coverage.
descriptionNullable:
This dataset is collected from onepiece.fandom.com (Thank you!)

This dataset contains the following columns:
**Kanji :** contain the title name of the episode in Japanese
**Romaji :** contain the title name of the episode in Romaji 
**Title :** the title of the episode
**Screenplay :** The person who is responsible for the screenplay of that episode.
**Art :** The person/people who is/are responsible for the art of that episode.
**Animation :** The person/people who is/are responsible for the key animation of that episode.
**Direction :** The person/people who is/are the director(s) of that episode.
**Chapter :** the page in manga chapter that this episode covered.
**Episode_num :** The episode number / The name of the episode  (There is a typo here, there are 5 episode that is not in a format "Episode #number", such as 

['Episode of East Blue',
 'Episode of Nami',
 'One Piece Film Strong World: Episode 0',
 'One Piece Film: Gold Episode 0',
 'One Piece: Romance Dawn Story'])

Note : When there are several chapter covered or several animator, this dataset will use ":::" to separate, since it's easier to distinguish , IMO.

Please let me know if there is any question.
